Job Overview
In response to our continued business expansion, we are seeking a skilled Structural Engineer to join our growing team. The successful candidate will be responsible for performing structural analysis and design for building and infrastructure projects, including reinforced concrete and streel structures, in compliance with applicable codes and standards.

Job description
• Perform structural analysis and design for building and infrastructure projects;
• Execute RC and steel structure design, including calculations, drawings, design reports, and specifications, in compliance with Eurocodes;
• Perform construction related services, including shop drawing reviews, responses to requests for information, and occasional specialized structural inspections;
• Create detailed structural drawings using CAD and BIM software (AutoCAD, Revit, etc.), ensuring all structural designs comply with relevant codes, standards, and project specifications;
• Provide technical support during project development and respond to design-related queries;
• Collaborate with architects, BIM teams, designers and building contractors to ensure proper design coordination and project execution;
• Support the team with other tasks as assigned by the Manager or Director.

1. Job Overview
In response to our continued business expansion, we are seeking a skilled BIM Modeler (Drafter) with a structural or civil engineering background to join our growing team. The successful candidate will be responsible for preparing accurate 2D and 3D models and drawings to support building and infrastructure projects. This role requires close collaboration with structural engineers, architects, and project stakeholders to ensure all deliverables meet technical standards and project requirements.

2. Job description
• Create and develop accurate, detailed 2D and 3D models based on design drawings, sketches, and engineering calculations;
• Collaborate with structural engineers and architects to interpret and implement design requirements;
• Ensure all drawings comply with relevant codes, standards, and project specifications;
• Revise and update models/drawings based on feedback from engineers, architects, and clients;
• Maintain well-organized documentation of drawings, revisions, and project records;
• Support the team with other tasks as assigned by Manager or Director.

